com.gif4j
Class MorphingFilter

java.lang.Object
  com.gif4j.MorphingFilter
Direct Known Subclasses:
CellFilter, CurtainFilter, MillFilter, MozaicFilter, RadarFilter, SnakeFilter, TunnelFilter
public abstract class MorphingFilter
extends java.lang.Object

MorphingFilter is the abstract base class for all morphing filters. Filters should subclass this class and override the methods which deal with the data that needs to be filtered and modify it as necessary.
It is meant to be used in conjunction with a GifImage and GifFrame objects.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Gif4J Software - Java GIF image processing solutions
See Also:
